sequenceDiagram
    participant K as Kafka Listener
    participant V as Validation Logic
    participant I as Incentive API<br/>localhost:8080/incentive
    participant D as H2 Database

    K->>V: Validate Transaction(senderId, recipientId, amount)
    V-->>K: Transaction valid
    K->>I: POST /incentive with Transaction JSON
    I-->>K: Incentive { amount }
    K->>D: Subtract transaction amount from sender
    K->>D: Add transaction amount + incentive to recipient
    K->>D: Save TransactionRecord(amount, incentive)
